OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1774980702
OL,3,CWhy the South of Scotland is key to
OL,4,Cthis regional Holyrood election
OL,6,FA memory has kept popping back into my
OL,7,Fhead over recent days.
OL,9,FIt was September 2024 and Sir Keir
OL,10,FStarmer was standing surrounded by
OL,11,FScottish political journalists in No
OL,12,F10 Downing Street.
OL,14,FHe had invited us in for, literally,
OL,15,Fbeer and sandwiches.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1774980702
OL,3,CWhy the South of Scotland is key to
OL,4,Cthis regional Holyrood election
OL,6,FI was still working for The Times
OL,7,Fnewspaper and was unexpectedly called
OL,8,Fto ask the first question, which was
OL,9,Fprobably a little more gung-ho for
OL,10,Fhaving consumed a bottle and a half of
OL,11,Flager.
OL,13,FPointing across the room towards Anas
OL,14,FSarwar and referencing the prime
OL,15,Fminister's statement that "things will
OL,16,Fget worse" before they get better and
OL,17,Fthe unpopular ` and later U-turned on
OL,18,F` decision to means-test winter fuel
OL,19,Fpayments for pensioners, I asked: "Do
OL,20,Fyou think your Eeyore government is
OL,21,Fharming Tigger over there?"
OL,26,@{D@cOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1774980702
OL,3,CWhy the South of Scotland is key to
OL,4,Cthis regional Holyrood election
OL,6,FThe Scottish Labour leader laughed
OL,7,Fheartily at the time but he has lost
OL,8,Fsome of that bounce over the last 18
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FAnd some of the ambition. And he
OL,12,Frecently tried to lose the prime
OL,13,Fminister.
OL,15,FSarwar still burns with a desire to be
OL,16,Ffirst minister.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1774980702
OL,3,CWhy the South of Scotland is key to
OL,4,Cthis regional Holyrood election
OL,6,FBut he has realised that to make that
OL,7,Fdream a reality he has to be extremely
OL,8,Feffective ` and fortunate ` in
OL,9,Fshrinking his party into one that is
OL,10,Ffocused on Greater Glasgow and Clyde,
OL,11,Fplus a sliver of urban centres in the
OL,12,Feast.
OL,14,FPollster Mark Diffley points out that
OL,15,Fthis is because Scotland's central
OL,16,Fbelt may be a small proportion of the
OL,17,Fcountry's land, but it is home to the
OL,18,Fvast majority of the population.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1774980702
OL,3,CWhy the South of Scotland is key to
OL,4,Cthis regional Holyrood election
OL,6,FHe says that Labour can still say they
OL,7,Fare speaking to most of the country,
OL,8,Fbut adds that if political parties are
OL,9,F"smart they will concentrate their
OL,10,Fresources accordingly".
OL,12,FAnd so Sarwar is far from alone in
OL,13,Fcontracting a once national beast into
OL,14,Fa tightly focused campaign operation.
OL,16,FThe Conservatives have largely
OL,17,Fretreated into defending their
OL,18,Fremaining strongholds in the south of
OL,19,FScotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
